{"id":8242,"date":"2026-02-03T10:11:04","date_gmt":"2026-02-03T03:11:04","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/?p=8242"},"modified":"2026-02-03T10:11:04","modified_gmt":"2026-02-03T03:11:04","slug":"sodium-hyaluronate-cap-am-sau-va-phuc-hoi","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/su-kien\/sodium-hyaluronate-cap-am-sau-va-phuc-hoi\/","title":{"rendered":"Sodium Hyaluronate \u2013 C\u1ea5p \u1ea9m s\u00e2u v\u00e0 ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i \u0111\u00e0n h\u1ed3i t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean c\u1ee7a da"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Khi n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 \u201cc\u1ea5p \u1ea9m\u201d, kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t n\u00e0o v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Sodium Hyaluronate, phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u01a1n c\u1ee7a Hyaluronic Acid (HA). Nh\u1edd kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u00fat n\u01b0\u1edbc g\u1ea5p h\u00e0ng ngh\u00ecn l\u1ea7n tr\u1ecdng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, n\u00f3 gi\u1eef cho da lu\u00f4n \u1ea9m, c\u0103ng v\u00e0 m\u1ec1m, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3.<\/span><\/p>\n\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"tong-quan-ve-sodium-hyaluronate\"><\/span><b>T\u1ed5ng quan v\u1ec1 Sodium Hyaluronate<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">T\u00ean khoa h\u1ecdc: Sodium Hyaluronate l\u00e0 d\u1ea1ng mu\u1ed1i natri c\u1ee7a Hyaluronic Acid, m\u1ed9t polysaccharide t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean c\u00f3 trong c\u01a1 th\u1ec3, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t \u1edf m\u00f4 li\u00ean k\u1ebft, d\u1ecbch kh\u1edbp v\u00e0 da.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ngu\u1ed3n g\u1ed1c \u2013 l\u1ecbch s\u1eed \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng: Ban \u0111\u1ea7u, HA \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebft xu\u1ea5t t\u1eeb m\u00e0o g\u00e0, sau n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t b\u1eb1ng c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 l\u00ean men vi sinh, gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9 tinh khi\u1ebft cao v\u00e0 an to\u00e0n h\u01a1n.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t v\u1edbi Hyaluronic Acid: Sodium Hyaluronate c\u00f3 k\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc ph\u00e2n t\u1eed nh\u1ecf h\u01a1n, tan t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n trong n\u01b0\u1edbc, v\u00e0 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u01a1n trong c\u00f4ng th\u1ee9c m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m, n\u00ean d\u1ec5 th\u1ea9m th\u1ea5u v\u00e0 ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 h\u01a1n tr\u00ean da.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><em>V\u00ec <span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Hyaluronic Acid quen thu\u1ed9c h\u01a1n n\u00ean m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i nh\u00e3n h\u00e0ng v\u1eabn s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng t\u00ean g\u1ecdi Hyaluronic Acid cho s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<\/span><\/em><\/p>\n<p><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-8244 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Sodium-Hyaluronate-2.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"880\" height=\"550\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Sodium-Hyaluronate-2.webp 880w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Sodium-Hyaluronate-2-300x300.webp 300w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Sodium-Hyaluronate-2-768x480.webp 768w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Sodium-Hyaluronate-2-600x375.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 880px) 100vw, 880px\"><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"dac-diem-hoat-chat-sodium-hyaluronate\"><\/span><b>\u0110\u1eb7c \u0111i\u1ec3m ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t Sodium Hyaluronate<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"cong-dung-noi-bat-cua-sodium-hyaluronate\"><\/span><b>C\u00f4ng d\u1ee5ng n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt c\u1ee7a Sodium Hyaluronate<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Sodium Hyaluronate c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng gi\u1eef n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 li\u00ean k\u1ebft \u1ea9m trong da, gi\u00fap b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t da m\u1ec1m, m\u1ecbn v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e0n h\u1ed3i h\u01a1n. N\u00f3 ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t \u201cmi\u1ebfng b\u1ecdt bi\u1ec3n sinh h\u1ecdc\u201d, h\u00fat v\u00e0 gi\u1eef n\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1eeb m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng ho\u1eb7c t\u1eeb t\u1ea7ng s\u00e2u c\u1ee7a da. Khi da \u0111\u1ee7 n\u01b0\u1edbc, h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 kh\u1ecfe h\u01a1n, t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng kh\u00f4, bong v\u1ea3y, ho\u1eb7c k\u00edch \u1ee9ng gi\u1ea3m r\u00f5 r\u1ec7t. Ngo\u00e0i ra, HA c\u00f2n gi\u00fap t\u0103ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 th\u1ea9m th\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t kh\u00e1c khi d\u00f9ng \u0111\u00fang th\u1ee9 t\u1ef1 v\u00e0 m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng pH ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"co-che-hoat-dong-cua-sodium-hyaluronate\"><\/span><b>C\u01a1 ch\u1ebf ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a Sodium Hyaluronate<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ph\u00e2n t\u1eed Sodium Hyaluronate li\u00ean k\u1ebft v\u1edbi n\u01b0\u1edbc trong m\u00f4 v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o l\u1edbp m\u00e0ng \u1ea9m m\u1ecfng tr\u00ean b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t da. L\u1edbp m\u00e0ng n\u00e0y gi\u00fap gi\u1ea3m m\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc qua bi\u1ec3u b\u00ec (TEWL), \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi gi\u1eef \u1ea9m v\u00e0 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c m\u1ecbn m\u00e0ng. \u1ede t\u1ea7ng s\u00e2u, ph\u00e2n t\u1eed nh\u1ecf h\u01a1n (low molecular weight HA) c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 len l\u1ecfi v\u00e0o l\u1edbp s\u1eebng, k\u00edch th\u00edch t\u1ebf b\u00e0o s\u1eebng ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3, g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n l\u00e0m da \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1eb7n v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e0n h\u1ed3i h\u01a1n.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"dang-bao-che-va-kich-thuoc-phan-tu-pho-bien\"><\/span><b>D\u1ea1ng b\u00e0o ch\u1ebf v\u00e0 k\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc ph\u00e2n t\u1eed ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><b>High Molecular Weight (HMW):<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> n\u1eb1m tr\u00ean b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t, gi\u1eef \u1ea9m t\u1ee9c th\u00ec, t\u1ea1o c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c c\u0103ng m\u1ecbn.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>Low Molecular Weight (LMW):<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> th\u1ea5m nh\u1eb9 h\u01a1n, gi\u00fap da ng\u1eadm n\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 gi\u1ea3m kh\u00f4 k\u00e9o d\u00e0i.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>Crosslinked HA (HA gel m\u1ea1ng l\u01b0\u1edbi):<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> b\u1ec1n h\u01a1n, th\u01b0\u1eddng d\u00f9ng trong serum cao c\u1ea5p ho\u1eb7c filler ti\u00eam y khoa (HA d\u1ea1ng ti\u00eam).<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Trong m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m b\u00f4i, c\u00e1c th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u th\u01b0\u1eddng d\u00f9ng h\u1ed7n h\u1ee3p nhi\u1ec1u lo\u1ea1i HA \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o <\/span><b>\u201c\u0111a t\u1ea7ng \u1ea9m\u201d<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> gi\u00fap da v\u1eeba m\u1ec1m m\u1ecbn b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t, v\u1eeba \u1ea9m s\u00e2u.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"luu-y-su-dung-sodium-hyaluronate\"><\/span><b>L\u01b0u \u00fd s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Sodium Hyaluronate<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"doi-tuong-su-dung\"><\/span><b>\u0110\u1ed1i t\u01b0\u1ee3ng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng\u00a0<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<figure id=\"attachment_8245\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-8245\" style=\"width: 880px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-8245 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Sodium-Hyaluronate-3.webp\" alt=\"\u0110\u1ed1i t\u01b0\u1ee3ng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Sodium Hyaluronate\" width=\"880\" height=\"550\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Sodium-Hyaluronate-3.webp 880w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Sodium-Hyaluronate-3-300x300.webp 300w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Sodium-Hyaluronate-3-768x480.webp 768w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Sodium-Hyaluronate-3-600x375.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 880px) 100vw, 880px\"><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-8245\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">\u0110\u1ed1i t\u01b0\u1ee3ng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Sodium Hyaluronate<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Da kh\u00f4, bong, c\u0103ng r\u00e1t sau r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t ho\u1eb7c \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m, da \u0111ang treatment (acid, retinol, peel).<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Da m\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc do kh\u00ed h\u1eadu, \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00f2a, ho\u1eb7c sau th\u1ee7 thu\u1eadt.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u00f9ng cho m\u1ecdi lo\u1ea1i da, k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 da d\u1ea7u \u2013 n\u1ebfu ch\u1ecdn c\u00f4ng th\u1ee9c nh\u1eb9, kh\u00f4ng b\u00edt t\u1eafc.<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><br \/>\n<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Xem th\u00eam: <a href=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/tinh-chat-cap-am-chuyen-sau-gsc\/\">Serum Sodium Hyaluronate GSC<\/a><\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"cach-dung-%e2%80%93-lieu-luong\"><\/span><b>C\u00e1ch d\u00f9ng \u2013 li\u1ec1u l\u01b0\u1ee3ng\u00a0<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Sodium Hyaluronate ph\u00e1t huy t\u1ed1i \u0111a khi thoa tr\u00ean da c\u00f2n h\u01a1i \u1ea9m, v\u00ec khi \u0111\u00f3 ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t c\u00f3 s\u1eb5n n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ec3 li\u00ean k\u1ebft. D\u01b0\u1ee1ng ch\u1ea5t n\u00e0y th\u01b0\u1eddng n\u1eb1m trong toner, essence, serum ho\u1eb7c kem d\u01b0\u1ee1ng. N\u00ean d\u00f9ng 1\u20132 l\u1ea7n m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y sau b\u01b0\u1edbc l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Tr\u00ecnh t\u1ef1 g\u1ee3i \u00fd: r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t \u2192 toner \u2192 serum Sodium Hyaluronate \u2192 kem d\u01b0\u1ee1ng kh\u00f3a \u1ea9m \u2192 kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng (ban ng\u00e0y).<\/span><\/p>\n<p><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">L\u01b0u \u00fd: N\u1ebfu d\u00f9ng \u1edf d\u1ea1ng tinh ch\u1ea5t ri\u00eang, n\u00ean thoa l\u1edbp m\u1ecfng v\u00e0 kh\u00f3a \u1ea9m ngay sau \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh hi\u1ec7n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00fat \u1ea9m ng\u01b0\u1ee3c khi kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed qu\u00e1 kh\u00f4.<\/span><\/i><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng th\u01b0\u1eddng nhanh, ch\u1ec9 sau v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y da \u0111\u00e3 m\u1ec1m v\u00e0 \u1ea9m h\u01a1n, c\u00f2n hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 r\u00f5 r\u1ec7t v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9 m\u1ecbn v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e0n h\u1ed3i th\u01b0\u1eddng th\u1ea5y sau 2\u20134 tu\u1ea7n d\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ec1u.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"phoi-hop-sodium-hyaluronate-hieu-qua\"><\/span><b>Ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p Sodium Hyaluronate hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><b>Sodium Hyaluronate + Ceramide:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> v\u1eeba gi\u1eef n\u01b0\u1edbc v\u1eeba c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o da.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>Sodium Hyaluronate + Panthenol (B5):<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> l\u00e0m d\u1ecbu v\u00e0 c\u1ea5p \u1ea9m s\u00e2u.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>Sodium Hyaluronate + Niacinamide:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t, gi\u00fap da s\u00e1ng v\u00e0 m\u01b0\u1ee3t.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>Sodium Hyaluronate + Retinol ho\u1eb7c AHA\/BHA:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> gi\u1ea3m kh\u00f4 bong, t\u0103ng dung n\u1ea1p treatment.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>Sodium Hyaluronate + Peptide:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i v\u00e0 t\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u00e0n h\u1ed3i da.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-8247 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Sodium-Hyaluronate-4.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"880\" height=\"550\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Sodium-Hyaluronate-4.webp 880w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Sodium-Hyaluronate-4-300x300.webp 300w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Sodium-Hyaluronate-4-768x480.webp 768w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Sodium-Hyaluronate-4-600x375.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 880px) 100vw, 880px\"><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"luu-y-chong-chi-dinh-sodium-hyaluronate\"><\/span><b>L\u01b0u \u00fd &amp; Ch\u1ed1ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ecbnh Sodium Hyaluronate<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Sodium Hyaluronate c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9 an to\u00e0n r\u1ea5t cao v\u00e0 hi\u1ebfm g\u00e2y d\u1ecb \u1ee9ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean, c\u00f3 v\u00e0i l\u01b0u \u00fd th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf khi d\u00f9ng:<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Khi m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng qu\u00e1 kh\u00f4, kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean d\u00f9ng HA \u0111\u01a1n l\u1ebb m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 l\u1edbp kem kh\u00f3a \u1ea9m. Trong \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed kh\u00f4, ph\u00e2n t\u1eed HA c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u00fat n\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1eeb ch\u00ednh l\u00e0n da ra ngo\u00e0i, khi\u1ebfn da kh\u00f4 ng\u01b0\u1ee3c.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Tr\u00e1nh d\u00f9ng c\u00f9ng l\u00fac v\u1edbi s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ee9a c\u1ed3n kh\u00f4 ho\u1eb7c h\u01b0\u01a1ng li\u1ec7u m\u1ea1nh, v\u00ec s\u1ebd l\u00e0m bay h\u01a1i n\u01b0\u1edbc nhanh, gi\u1ea3m hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 c\u1ea5p \u1ea9m.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ch\u1ecdn c\u00f4ng th\u1ee9c c\u00f3 t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 v\u00e0 tr\u1ecdng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng ph\u00e2n t\u1eed \u0111a d\u1ea1ng, tr\u00e1nh s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ee9a HA n\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9 qu\u00e1 cao nh\u01b0ng thi\u1ebfu n\u1ec1n d\u01b0\u1ee1ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Sau peel, laser ho\u1eb7c vi\u00eam \u0111\u1ecf, n\u00ean d\u00f9ng HA thu\u1ea7n ho\u1eb7c ph\u1ed1i ceramide\/panthenol, kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean d\u00f9ng d\u1ea1ng HA k\u00e8m acid m\u1ea1nh.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_8246\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-8246\" style=\"width: 880px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-8246 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Sodium-Hyaluronate-4-copy.webp\" alt=\"Ph\u1ee5 n\u1eef c\u00f3 thai v\u00e0 cho con b\u00fa c\u00f3 d\u00f9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Sodium Hyaluronate kh\u00f4ng?\" width=\"880\" height=\"550\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Sodium-Hyaluronate-4-copy.webp 880w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Sodium-Hyaluronate-4-copy-300x300.webp 300w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Sodium-Hyaluronate-4-copy-768x480.webp 768w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Sodium-Hyaluronate-4-copy-600x375.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 880px) 100vw, 880px\"><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-8246\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Ph\u1ee5 n\u1eef c\u00f3 thai v\u00e0 cho con b\u00fa c\u00f3 d\u00f9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Sodium Hyaluronate kh\u00f4ng?<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><b><\/b><b><br \/>\n<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u00f3. Sodium Hyaluronate l\u00e0 ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean c\u00f3 trong c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi, an to\u00e0n khi d\u00f9ng ngo\u00e0i da, k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 trong thai k\u1ef3 ho\u1eb7c giai \u0111o\u1ea1n cho con b\u00fa. C\u00e1c d\u00f2ng serum, kem d\u01b0\u1ee1ng, m\u1eb7t n\u1ea1 ch\u1ee9a HA \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng h\u00e0ng ng\u00e0y.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>T\u00e0i li\u1ec7u tham kh\u1ea3o:<\/p>\n<p><i>Dr. Lida \u00c7iteli<\/i>. (2025). Dr. Lida \u00c7iteli Istanbul. <a href=\"https:\/\/www.drlidaciteli.com\/what-is-sodium-hyaluronate-how-is-it-used-in-skincare\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">https:\/\/www.drlidaciteli.com\/what-is-sodium-hyaluronate-how-is-it-used-in-skincare<\/a><\/p>\n<p>\u200c<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p> Sodium Hyaluronate \u2013 d\u1ea1ng mu\u1ed1i \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a Hyaluronic Acid gi\u00fap c\u1ea5p \u1ea9m s\u00e2u, gi\u1eef n\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 l\u00e0m d\u1ecbu da.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":12,"featured_media":8243,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[1],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-8242","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-su-kien"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/8242","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/12"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=8242"}],"version-history":[{"count":3,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/8242\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":8920,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/8242\/revisions\/8920"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/8243"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=8242"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=8242"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=8242"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org